- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is a possible category as the paper applies machine learning techniques to healthcare data.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the importance of interpretability and decision making in healthcare systems.
